@startuml ADR-000003-sni-routing
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title SNI-маршрутизация через nginx stream (L4)\n(access node)

participant "Входящее\nTLS-соединение\n:443" as tls
participant "nginx stream\n(ssl_preread)" as nginx
participant "Squid Access\n127.0.0.1:3128" as squid
participant "TLS Relay\n127.0.0.1:9443" as relay

tls -> nginx : TLS ClientHello\n(SNI: api.anthropic.com)
nginx -> nginx : ssl_preread on\n$ssl_preread_server_name\n= "api.anthropic.com"
nginx -> nginx : map lookup:\ndefault → fallback_squid
nginx -> squid : proxy_pass fallback_squid\n(PROXY protocol,\nбез расшифровки TLS)

note over nginx, squid : End-to-end TLS сохраняется

== Пример: Telegram (fake-TLS) ==

tls -> nginx : TLS ClientHello\n(SNI: example.gov.ru)
nginx -> nginx : ssl_preread on\n$ssl_preread_server_name\n= "example.gov.ru"
nginx -> nginx : map lookup:\nexample.gov.ru → aiproxy_mtproxy
nginx -> relay : proxy_pass aiproxy_mtproxy\n(→ TLS relay :9443)

note over relay
  TLS relay оборачивает поток
  в TLS 1.3 (proxy_ssl on) и
  пересылает на upstream :443
end note

== Пример: default (неизвестный SNI) ==

tls -> nginx : TLS ClientHello\n(SNI: unknown.com)
nginx -> nginx : map lookup:\ndefault → fallback_squid
nginx -> squid : proxy_pass fallback_squid

@enduml
